<h1>Missing Write Access</h1>
<p>In order for <a href="http://graffiticms.com">Graffiti CMS</a> to properly function, it will need <strong>write access</strong> to server's file system. You will not be able to add categories, write/edit posts, or upload files until this issue is corrected</p>
<p>If you are unsure how to enable this, please see the article, "<em><a href="http://docs.GraffitiCMS.com/documentation/configure-server/">How to Configure Your Server For Graffiti</a></em>" on <a href="http://docs.GraffitiCMS.com">docs.GraffitiCMS.com</a>.</p>

